seo: OpenSSH,漏洞检测,CVE合规检查,端口扫描,安全漏洞
seo_en: OpenSSH, vulnerability detection, CVE compliance check, port scanning, security vulnerabilities
summary: 该插件用于检测OpenSSH相关的CVE漏洞，涵盖2010年至2021年的多个CVE编号，通过匹配版本号来识别潜在的安全问题。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect OpenSSH-related CVE vulnerabilities, covering multiple CVE numbers from 2010 to 2021, identifying potential security issues by matching version numbers.
